long_description:
Citrus Ginger Hand Wash 8 oz Gel

About Skin By Ann Webb Anns passion for developing optimal skin care began at an early age. Her own struggles with cystic acne were the driving force behind her passion for finding a solution to heal and develop beautiful skin. Ann traveled far beyond her small town of Gueydan, Louisiana to research and educate herself about every type of skin treatment available. She discovered that most treatment protocols were limited to a topical medication and antibiotics until she met Dr. Brent Schillinger. She was fascinated by his hands-on, specialized acne treatments that finally brought about a positive change in her skin. This fateful meeting began her journey into the world of esthetics. Ann went on to work for the PGA Spa, The Florida Center of Cosmetic Surgery, and to serve as Cosmetic Director for the Austin Plastic Surgery Center while maintaining an esthetics studio in her home. Developing a product line came about when she recognized a need for affordable, clean products for her local esthetics clients. She had already contributed to the development of two other product lines, and was ready to put more than 10 years of research and labor into a line of her own. Ann envisioned products that would be affordable, simple to use, and contain the best pharmaceutical-grade ingredients available. She turned to her best friend, Joanna Marceaux, who had worked for more than 8 years as a business development specialist for guidance. With Joannas help, Skin By Ann Webb was born. As life-long friends, Ann and Joanna have established a successful business partnership and have grown Skin By Ann Webb together Ann and Joanna continue to direct the Skin By Ann Webb product line nationwide. Anns true passion still lies in her own treatment spa located in Austin, Texas, where she combines more than 15 years of research and hands-on training with her own protocols for treating skin. When Ann is not in her clinic she spends quality time with her boys.

title: InstaNatural Fractionated Coconut Oil - 100% Pure - Liquid Moisturizer for Skin, Face, Body & Nails - 16 OZ
short_description:
• Naturally rich in Vitamin E for antioxidant defense
  • Nourishing conditioner for dry and damaged hair
  • Provides unsurpassed moisture for the skin
long_description:
InstaNatural's 100% Pure Fractionated Coconut Oil is a refreshing multi-purpose oil that offers a wide range of nourishing benefits for the face, body and hair. Apply on your entire body to soften and moisturize dry, rough skin. This versatile oil also acts as an ultra-hydrating conditioner for dry or damaged hair. Moreover, Coconut Oil is superb for aromatherapy and massages since it serves as a great base or carrier oil.

KEY FEATURES:

  • Refreshes & Hydrates Head to Toe - InstaNatural's Fractionated Coconut Oil is a 100% pure product that instills unsurpassed moisture and softness for men and women with dry and rough skin on the face and body. This coconut oil comes in a lightweight formula, which makes it easy to use and apply anywhere from your face to your hands to your feet and ensures that you'll see a wealth of results no matter how you choose to use it.
  • Packed with Antioxidants - Not only is this coconut oil lightweight, making it fast-absorbing and non-greasy, it's also packed with antioxidants from the Vitamin E coconuts contain. This means that InstaNatural's formula provides your skin with ultimate defense against signs of aging, sun damage from harmful UV rays and will even help ease irritating skin concerns, giving you softer and smoother skin in a simple but powerful product.
  • Restore Dry & Lifeless Hair - This pure and fractionated coconut oil is perfect as a nourishing conditioner to remedy dry and damaged hair because it provides the moisture your hair needs to regain its soft silkiness and shine that it may have lost from overexposure to heat or styling products. It'll also fight frizz all day long when just a little is applied after your shampoo.
  • Pure & Premium Formula - InstaNatural only extracts the most nourishing liquid from coconuts (Cocos Nucifer) to ensure that your skin, hair and nails receive the best possible nourishment without any unwanted toxins or pesticides. By giving you only the most premium ingredients, you're sure to see the enhanced skin care results quickly and easily.
  • Best All-Around Oil - This coconut oil isn't just good for making your skin softer and your hair healthier; it has a ton of other unconventional DIY uses that may shock you at first but will leave you pleasantly surprised. You can use this product as a great stimulating massage oil, lip balm, shave gel, makeup remover, nail strengthener, cuticle softener and more.

Ingredients:
100% Pure Fractionated Coconut Oil (Cocos Nucifera).

Directions:
Skin Care Application:
Press 2-3 drops between your palms and massage onto cleansed skin. Best applied after a serum and before a moisturizer. May also be mixed into your favorite facial mask or scrub for added moisture.

Body Care Application:
Press 1-2 pumps between your palms and massage onto cleansed and slightly damp skin. Best applied directly after a shower. For maximum hydration, add to a warm bath and soak for up to 30 minutes

Hair Care Application:
Press oil between your palms, massage onto dry scalp and comb to distribute evenly. Allow oil to soak for up to 30 minutes. Shampoo thoroughly to remove. May also be applied to split ends to hydrate and soften.

Nail Care Application:
Massage 1-2 drops around cuticles and fingertips. For best results, apply nightly. May also be mixed into a hand cream for additional nourishment.

Your skin (often exposed to heat, cold, dirt and harsh detergents) is one of the first areas of the body to show aging. Like a breath of fresh air, this new product will make a noticeable difference from the very first time you use it!  It will jump start your day while simultaneously treating your skin to a rich infusion of relaxation.  
 
This revolutionary product is the first of it's kind!  It is the only product that can be used to safely wash your face, hands and body.  Specifically formulated for today's busy male, it will simplify your life by reducing bathroom clutter as well as necessary travel companions.   Now you can eliminate 4 different products (facial cleanser, acne cleanser, liquid hand soap, body wash) and replace them with this hard-working wash for the active man.
 
More gentle than other washes, it will leave your skin feeling energized and refreshed with a sublimely uplifting feeling. Naturally hypoallergenic and extensively tested, you ' ll love this  wash.  The neaclear Liquid Oxygen Wash is our most popular product for men!
 
A truly unique wash created to turn daily showering into an extraordinarily transforming and luxurious experience. Gentle, yet effective, this mixture feels like sumptuous clouds of lather, leaving skin soft, refreshed and subtly scented. This formula is ideal for use in all environments and with all skin types.   The neaclear Wash is enriched with pure, natural ingredients to cleanse, moisturize and gently care for male skin. The difference is immediately obvious. The nourishment lasts for hours.  It is strongly recommended by plastic surgeons and dermatologists.  
Infused with Oxygenated Purified Water to introduce a powerful boost of oxygen into your skin's cells as you wash, this Body Wash will leave your skin feeling clean and energized. We have also enhanced this new product with Vitamins A & D (to replenish these nutrients which are lost to the harsh and sometimes toxic conditions we expose our skin to everyday), Vitamin C & E (two of the most effective anti-aging treatments for your skin) & Aloe Vera (to soothe your skin while you use).  Vitamin A aids in cell function and keeps the skin healthy, clear and infection resistant.  Vitamin D helps to protect the cellular membrane from free radical damage.  Vitamin C inhibits sun damage caused by harmful UVA and UVB rays. Vitamin C is also photo-protective, especially when used in conjunction with a broad-based sun block.  Vitamin E is considered to be the most important oil soluble vitamin and free radical scavenger.  Moisturizing base of pure food-grade Aloe Vera assists in soothing irritated skin.
 
As if that wasn't enough, to make this product even better we have made O 2 Power fragrance-free and hypoallergenic .

title: Nubian Heritage Hand Cream 4oz 1pc
short_description: Nubian Heritage Hand Cream 4oz 1pc
long_description:
With oats, aloe vera & sandalwood oil. Acne-fighting, detoxifying & healing. Certified organic ingredients. Our Oats & Aloe Hand Cream is a nutrient-rich long lasting moisture treatment. This all-natural recipe is fortified with multi-vitamins, oat flour, vegetable butters and vegetable oils to repair, moisturize, and strengthen hard-working hands. Humble Beginnings: In 1992, fresh out of college without jobs, Rich and Nyema embarked on a personal mission to product high quality bath and body products utilizing all-natural ingredients and ancient healing philosophies from around the globe. Nubian Heritage is the brainchild of these lifelong friends, turned New York Street Vendors, who simply grew frustrated with the inferior quality, high chemical content, poor selection and exorbitant prices of skin care products. Today Nubian Heritage has hundreds of all-natural and organic products and although they are no longer made in bath tubs or kitchen sinks, little else has changed. They are still obsessed with Fair Trade ingredients, ancient healing philosophies, community commerce and culturally authentic products. Heritage: African Black Soap, made from palm ash, tamarind extract, tar and plantain peel has been used in Africa for centuries to treat eczema, acne, oily skin, psoriasis, and other skin ailments. Historical references to shea butter, a staple of African pharmacology, date back to the reported shea butter caravans of Cleopatras Egypt. Cruelty free. www.NubianHeritage.com. Made in the USA.
• Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea Butter [Certified Organic Ingredient]), Deionized Water, Stearyl Alcohol (Palm Kernel), Ceteareth 20 (Emulsifying Wax), Mangifera Indica (Mango) Seed Butter (Certified Organic Ingredient), Theobroma Cacao (Cocoa) Seed Butter (Certified Organic Ingredient), African Black Soap Extract, Avena Sativa (Oat) Kernel Meal, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice (Certified Organic Ingredient), Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Carbomer, Vegetable Glycerin, Jojoba Oil (Certified Organic Ingredient), Salicylic Acid, Santalum Album (Sandalwood) Oil, Essential Oil Blend.

short_description: • Pack of 6
long_description:
• Pack of 6 for the UPC: 351672203566


    •  
    Vaginal Cream
    Taro Pharm
    Active Ingredients:
    Miconazole Nitrate 2% (100 mg Per Dose)
    Before using, read the enclosed educational brochure. IF THIS IS THE FIRST TIME YOU HAVE HAD VAGINAL OR VULVAR ITCH AND DISCOMFORT, CONSULT YOUR DOCTOR. IF YOU HAVE HAD A DOCTOR DIAGNOSE A VAGINAL YEAST INFECTION BEFORE AND HAVE THE SAME SYMPTOMS NOW, USE THIS CREAM AS DIRECTED FOR SEVEN CONSECUTIVE DAYS. FOR VAGINAL USE ONLY. DO NOT USE IN EYES OR TAKE BY MOUTH. Insert 1 applicatorful of cream into the vagina at bedtime for 7 nights in a row. Squeeze a small amount of cream onto your finger and gently spread the cream onto the affected area of the vulva twice daily (morning and bedtime) for up to 7 days as needed to relieve external vulvar itching. THE CREAM SHOULD NOT BE USED FOR VULVAR ITCHING DUE TO CAUSES OTHER THAN A YEAST INFECTION. Applicator and instructions are enclosed.
    Inactive Ingredients:
    Apricot Kernel Oil/PEG-6; Butylated Hydroxytoluene; Mineral Oil; PEG-6-32 Stearate/Glycol Stearate; Purified Water; Benzoic Acid (0.20%) as a Preservative
    Uses:
    For the treatment of vaginal yeast infections (candidiasis) and the relief of external vulvar itching and irritation associated with a yeast infection.
    DO NOT USE MICONAZOLE NITRATE VAGINAL CREAM IF YOU HAVE ANY OF THE SIGNS AND SYMPTOMS LISTED BELOW. ALSO, IF THEY OCCUR WHILE USING MICONAZOLE NITRATE VAGINAL CREAM, STOP USING THE PRODUCT AND CONTACT YOUR DOCTOR RIGHT AWAY. YOU MAY HAVE A MORE SERIOUS ILLNESS. FEVER (HIGHER THAN 100 DEGREES ORALLY). PAIN IN THE LOWER ABDOMEN, BACK, OR EITHER SHOULDER. A VAGINAL DISCHARGE THAT SMELLS BAD. IF YOU DO NOT IMPROVE IN 3 DAYS, OR IF YOU DO NOT GET WELL IN 7 DAYS, YOU MAY HAVE A CONDITION OTHER THAN A YEAST INFECTION. CONSULT YOUR DOCTOR. If your symptoms return within two months or if you have infections that do not clear up easily with proper treatment, consult your doctor. You could be pregnant or there could be a serious underlying medical cause for your infections, including diabetes or a damaged immune system (including damage from infection with HIV - the virus that causes AIDS). (PLEASE READ EDUCATIONAL BROCHURE FOUND INSIDE PACKAGE.) Mineral oil may weaken latex in condoms or in diaphragms. This cream contains mineral oil. Do not rely on condoms or diaphragms to prevent sexually transmitted diseases or pregnancy while using miconazole nitrate vaginal cream. Do not use tampons while using this medication. DO NOT USE IN GIRLS LESS THAN 12 YEARS OF AGE. If you are pregnant or think you may be pregnant, do not use this product except under the advice and supervision of a doctor. Keep this and all drugs out of the reach of children. In case of accidental ingestion, seek professional assistance or contact a poison control center immediately.

short_description: Soften and smooth the appearance of lines, and fully nourish skin.
long_description:
UPC: 028367831969 - Kiss My Face Potent And Pure Under Age Ultra Hydrating Skin Moisturizer - 1 Oz, 2 Pack - Soften and smooth the appearance of lines, and fully nourish skin. -

INDICATIONS:

Kiss My Face paraben free sunspray lotion water resistant, SPF 30

It is an easy to apply sunscreen that offers paraben free, fragrance free, UVA and UVB protection. Plus Kiss My Face Sunspray Lotion is water resistant and fragrance free. A perfect sunscreen for those who play hard and enjoy the outdoors!

  • Great for Kids too!
  • Paraben Free
  • UVA/UVB Protection
  • Water Resistant
  • SPF 30
Uses:
  • Helps prevent sunburn
  • Higher SPF gives more sunburn protection
  • Retains SPF after 40 minutes of activity in water

INGREDIENTS:

Active Ingredients

Octinoxate 7.5%, Octisalate 5%, Zinc Oxide 1.7%.

Inactive Ingredients

Aqua, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Leaf Juice, Polysorbate-20, Cetearyl Alcohol, Acrylates Copolymer, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Glycerin, Dimethicone, Cetearyl Olivate, Sorbitan Olivate, Camellia Sinensis (Green Tea) Leaf Extract, Carota Sativa (Carrot) Extract, Tocopheryl Acetate (Vitamin E), Retinyl Palmitate (Vitamin A), Agaricus Bisporus (Mushroom) Betaglucans, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin.

DIRECTIONS:

Spray liberally. Sun conservatively. Reapply when playing hard or swimming. Shake well.

Apply liberally 20 minutes before sun exposure and as needed. Children under 6 months of age: ask a doctor. Spray 6-8 inches from skin and rub in. Do not spray directly onto face. Reapply as needed or after swimming, towel drying or excessive perspiration.

Sun Alert: Limiting sun exposure, wearing protective clothing and using suncreen may reduce the risk of skin aging, skin cancer and other harmful effects of the sun.

WARNINGS:

For external use only. When using this product keep out of eyes. Rinse with water to remove. Stop use and ask doctor if rash or irritation develops and lasts. Keep out of reach of children. If swallowed, get medical help or contact a Poison Control Center right away.

Tom's aluminum-free Natural Long-Lasting Deodorant uses all three ways to keep you smelling fresh, naturally. The top notes are a rainstorm of nutmeg, orange blossom, jasmine and gardenia, all of which instantly dissolve into the sweetness of a rich, fruity glow. Tuberose takes center stage, characterized by a hint of violet and soft nutty tones. The final bars are those of exotic amber, sandalwood and the warmth of vanilla benzoin. The french fashion house rochas was founded by marcel rochas in 1925. His forward-thinking fashions for women honored traditional feminine shapes. He even anticipated the needs of modern 20th-century women by designing skirts with pockets and mid-length coats. Perhaps his most famous design was the mermaid dress, which continues to inspire women's fashions today. The company increased its product line to incorporate fragrances in 1934. Anti-Wrinkle Deep Wrinkle Serum: Works hard on even the most frustrating wrinkles to uncover vibrant, healthier-looking skin starting in just 2 weeks. Multi-vitamin complex: boosts skin with anti-oxidants to help neutralize skin-damaging free radicals. Retinol SA: The patented Sustained Action works to continuously renew the look of skin throughout the day, helping smooth wrinkles fast and diminish the look of age spots. Skin conditioners: cushion skin as they hydrate, replenish and revitalize with line-plumping moisture.
    You may experience mild redness, a warm, tingling sensation or flaking (skin exfoliating). These are normal, temporary indications that the formula is working. If effects persist or cause discomfort, limit use to once every 2 to 3 days until your skin adjusts, then revert to daily use.

short_description: GreenAir Scent Pod Oil Diffuser Advanced Wellness Instant Healthful Mist Therapy
long_description:
1 - GreenAir Scent Pod Oil Diffuser Advanced Wellness Instant Healthful Mist Therapy

Want compact and portable access to your essential oils? The Scent Pod allows you to take your aromatherapy options on the go! Simply add a few drops of your favorite essential oil to the replaceable fiber pad, and it will INSTANTLY deliver the benefits of aromatherapy. NO WATER NEEDED.

The Scent Pod's small sleek design lends its versatility to be used anywhere. Use it in the office on your desk! Use it next to you while you watch TV! Use it in the Car! Use it while you are commuting to work on the train! The options are endless with the portability that it gives you with its multiple power options.

The Scent Pod's power adaptability makes it capable of being used anywhere. Use it with two AA batteries, a USB adapter, or an AC adapter (not included). It is a great option for the office, travel or any small space. The internal silent fan gently disperses the essential oil in the air. Take it with you wherever you go!

The Scent Pod comes packaged with the unit itself, two scent pads and a USB adapter. It DOES NOT come with an AC adapter.

Why Should You Diffuse?
Essential Oils have been shown to have a variety of effects throughout our lives. Diffusing Essential Oils gives you a way to deliver those oils into your system. Whether it is increasing relaxation, decreasing stress, or increasing focus - using the Scent Pod to deliver those benefits adds a spa-like atmosphere anywhere.

INDICATIONS:

Triple Action Stri-Dex Sensitive Skin Formula contains aloe, and is designed to gently clean your skin. An effective acne-fighting medication works to treat and help prevent pimples. cleanse the skin thoroughly before applying medication. use the pad to wipe the entire affected area. repeat with a clean pad as necessary to remove remaining traces of dirt. because excessive drying of the skin may occur, start with one application daily, then gradually increase to two to three times daily as needed or as directed by a doctor. if bothersome dryness or peeling occurs, reduce application to once a day or every other day. do not leave pad on skin for an extended period of time.

WARNINGS:
For External Use Only. Keep away from eyes, lips and other mucous membranes. Allergy alert: do not use this product if you have a known allergy to salicylic acid. Keep this and all drugs out of the reach of children.

These lint free cleaning cloths absorb up to eight times their own weight in liquid, and they dry twice as fast as an ordinary cotton towel or rag. They are machine washable and reusable for added convenience. Each unit comes with 12 colorful towels. Colors may vary.

long_description: Details: Botanical Name: Nepeta cataria. Origin: Canada.  Extraction Method: Steam Distilled.  Plant Part: Ariel parts  Strength of Aroma: Medium. Aromatic Scent:  Catnip essential oil has a green, herbaceous-floral scent.  Blends well with: Bergamot, Citronella, Clary sage, Helichrysum, Lavender, Lemon, Rosalina, Sandalwood and Turmeric.  Suggested Uses: Catnip is commonly used as an insect repellent. It has also been known to help with sleep and restlessness. Diffuse at night to help induce sleep. Add equal parts Catnip and Citronella to water or witch hazel for an all-natural insect repellent. To ease a headache or coughing, add a small amount to a carrier oil and apply to affected area.  Cautions: Possible skin sensitizaion.  Please Note: The International Federation of Aromatherapists does not recommend that Essential Oils be taken internally unless under the supervision of a Medical Doctor who is also qualified in clinical Aromatherapy.
